text: Mieczysław Długoborski was a middle-distance runner from Poland. Długoborski competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics. He was born on 10 January 1931 and died on 4 April 2020.Mieczysław Długoborski == References == Category:1931 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Polish middle-distance runners Category:Olympians for Poland
